<template>
    <section class="container">
        <v-calendar is-expanded :attributes='attrs'/>
    </section>
    
</template>

<style scoped>

</style>

<script>
export default  {
    data() {
    return {
      attrs: [
        {
          key: 'today',
          highlight: true,
          dates: new Date(),
        },
        {
          key: 'today1',
          highlight: true,
          dates: new Date(year(),month(),6),
        },
      ],
    };
  },
}
</script>
